title: ***Save $500 W/ Our Rent Special!*** HUB APARTMENTS
posting_body: ['***RENT SPECIAL: $400 RENT CREDIT + ADDTIONAL $100 IF YOU APPLY THE SAME DAY AS YOUR SHOWING!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS', 'Hub Apartments offers 1 bedroom apartments homes for rent in Richfield, MN.', 'Located on W. 65th Street adjacent to the Hub Shopping Center.', 'They are within walking distance to many restaurants, shops, recreational opportunities, the bus line and much more.', 'Easy freeway access to downtown Minneapolis, Edina, Bloomington and Mall of America.', 'Call today and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community.', 'Christopherson Properties:', 'show contact info', '1 BR - Deposit starts at $400', 'Lease Terms: Month-to-Month Rental Agreement with a 9 Month Clause', '$40 Application Fee per Adult', 'Cats Accepted with the Following Restrictions:', '$250 non-refundable pet fee, $30 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats per unit, and must be spayed/neutered.', 'Amenities:', '*Amazing Professional Staff That Understands That Service Counts', '*Expert Maintenance Team with 24-Hour Emergency Assistance Available', '*Heat, Trash, Gas, Water and Sewer Paid', '*Window Coverings', '*Ceiling Fans', '*Ample Closet Space', '*Picnic Area', '*Control Access Entries', '*Additional Storage', 'Year Built: 1960', '# of Buildings: 3', 'School District: Richfield', 'Bus Lines: 18, 68', 'Number of Floors: 3', 'Parking: Off-Street Parking', 'Garages: None', 'Laundry:', 'On-site, First Floor- Coin Operated', 'Cable TV: Cable and Internet Ready', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.']
